node.text:
People expect the most promising resort in Russia. This is a new resort "Dolina Vasta" ⛷ 🏂 

The project implies for the creation of the necessary tourist infrastructure for health and ski recreation in 2021-2025. 

Balneology centers with a sanatorium, boarding houses and spa hotels will be created on the territory of the Sochi National Park. In addition, a ski center with 80 km long tracks and several ski lifts with a total length of 13 km will be built. 

The companies "Interros" and "Vasta Discovery" and the state corporation VEB. RF are involved in the project.

#DolinaVasta #Sochi #Interros
